# LEGACY — pre per-project-container multi-project mode (one container fanning
# out across several projects' task APIs). It still works, but the recommended
# way to run multiple projects is now ONE runner container per project: create a
# config/projects/<name>/ directory (copy config/projects/example/) and generate
# the stack with scripts/gen-compose.sh. See the README "Multiple projects".
#
# Legacy format: copy to `config/projects.list` (gitignored), one line per
# project as: <slug> <token> [agent]. Only used when PROJECT_SLUG/PROJECT_TOKEN
# are empty. Lines starting with # and blank lines are ignored.
#
# my-first-project-ab3x9   abcdef0123456789...token...
# another-project-qz7k1    fedcba9876543210...token...   codex
